OL,3,CDIY heart monitor rolled out to cut
OL,4,Chospital waiting lists
OL,6,FAfter the new tool is worn for a few
OL,7,Fdays, patients can post the device
OL,8,Fback ` which will cut out the need for
OL,9,Fappointments to fit and remove the
OL,10,Fequipment.
OL,12,FThe information from the monitor is
OL,13,Fthen assessed using an artificial
OL,14,Fintelligence (AI) tool, Cardiologs,
OL,15,Fwhich produces a report which is then
OL,16,Fassessed by either a physiologist or a
OL,17,Fdoctor.
