OL,3,CDIY heart monitor rolled out to cut
OL,4,Chospital waiting lists
OL,6,FIt can be used to investigate
OL,7,Fconditions including atrial
OL,8,Ffibrillation, tachycardia or heart
OL,9,Fblocks.
OL,11,FFrimley Health NHS Foundation Trust
OL,12,Fprovides NHS hospital services for
OL,13,F900,000 people in Berkshire,
OL,14,FHampshire, Surrey, and South
OL,15,FBuckinghamshire and is the first trust
OL,16,Fin the country to roll out the device.
OL,18,FIt hopes the device will soon be used
OL,19,Facross other NHS trusts.
