OL,3,CDIY heart monitor rolled out to cut
OL,4,Chospital waiting lists
OL,6,FThe Trust said it will still use
OL,7,Ftraditional devices, known as Holter
OL,8,Fmonitors, on some patients who are in
OL,9,Fhospital, but many of those who are
OL,10,Foutside of hospital will be able to
OL,11,Faccess the new ePatch, which is made
OL,12,Fby Philips, to use in the comfort of
OL,13,Ftheir own homes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
