OL,3,CDIY heart monitor rolled out to cut
OL,4,Chospital waiting lists
OL,6,FDr Iain Sim, consultant cardiac
OL,7,Felectrophysiologist, said: "The
OL,8,Fpurpose of the device is to record the
OL,9,Fheart rhythm ` to collect electrical
OL,10,Fsignals from the heart ` and to try to
OL,11,Funderstand a bit about the patient and
OL,12,Fwhat they are experiencing and whether
OL,13,Fthat can be explained by their heart
OL,14,Frhythm.
OL,16,F"This smaller device allows us to
OL,17,Fmeasure at the moment up to 10 days.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
