OL,3,CDIY heart monitor rolled out to cut
OL,4,Chospital waiting lists
OL,6,F"The benefits of it are that it is
OL,7,Fsmaller and more convenient, rather
OL,8,Fthan different wires all over the
OL,9,Fplace.
OL,11,F"We are able to put them on faster and
OL,12,Fwe're able to reduce our turnaround
OL,13,Ftimes for reports and to get results
OL,14,Fback to patients faster."
OL,16,FHe said that traditional Holter
OL,17,Fmonitors are attached by trained
OL,18,Fphysiologists but there is a shortage
OL,19,Fof these staff members at present.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
