OL,3,CDIY heart monitor rolled out to cut
OL,4,Chospital waiting lists
OL,6,F"Because these are more
OL,7,Fstraightforward, we've got specialist
OL,8,Fnurses who can be quite easily trained
OL,9,Fto apply them," he added.
OL,11,FSuzanne Jordan, associate director for
OL,12,Fmedicine at Frimley Health, said the
OL,13,Fpatches can even be sent out to
OL,14,Fpatients for them to attach themselves.
OL,16,FThe feedback from the monitors are
OL,17,Fdeveloped into reports for medics
OL,18,Fwhich are categorised in a traffic
OL,19,Flight system, she said.
