OL,3,CDIY heart monitor rolled out to cut
OL,4,Chospital waiting lists
OL,6,F"Green is perfectly fine ` within
OL,7,Fnormal limits; amber may need a
OL,8,Fclinician to review the report; red
OL,9,Fmeans potentially significant pauses
OL,10,For arrhythmia that need kind of an
OL,11,Furgent review," she said.
OL,13,F"It's been really positive ` staff and
OL,14,Fpatients really like it.
OL,16,F"We can post the patches to patients `
OL,17,Fthere's explicit instructions there in
OL,18,Fterms of how to put it on, what to do
OL,19,Fif there's a problem, and also just to
OL,20,Fsend it back as well.
