OL,6,F"Once it comes back, it gets
OL,7,Fdownloaded and the turnaround times
OL,8,Fare great."
OL,10,FMs Jordan added: "If you think of the
OL,11,Fbigger picture, it means that we're
OL,12,Fgoing to be able to manage our
OL,13,Fpatients quickly.
OL,15,F"We've been running clinics by seeing
OL,16,Fmaybe 30 patients in one day, whereas
OL,17,Fbefore, we were probably seeing 14
OL,18,Fmaximum ` so we've kind of doubled our
OL,19,Fproductivity."
